ğŸš« Why You Canâ€™t Directly Link ChatGPT Plus to Your Addon
Hereâ€™s the deal:


Feature	ChatGPT Plus (chat.openai.com)	OpenAI API
âœ… Chat in browser	Yes	No
âœ… Use GPT-4	Yes	Yes (with cost)
âœ… Use in your own code	âŒ	âœ…
âœ… Generate custom content (like catalogs)	âŒ	âœ…
âœ… Authentication with API keys	âŒ	âœ…
ChatGPT Plus doesnâ€™t give you an API key, and OpenAI intentionally separates the accounts for security and monetization reasons.

ğŸŒ€ What Could Work (Risky or Hacky Paths)
âš ï¸ Option 1: Browser Automation (Unofficial, Fragile)
You could technically:

Use Puppeteer or Playwright (Node.js browser automation tools)

